    <p>{`Sauce Labs Testrunner Toolkit is designed to support native Javascript frameworks through a containerized testing solution that simplifies user set up and speeds up test execution time. `}</p>
    <p>{`This approach combines the power and expressiveness of different test frameworks with the dashboards, infrastructure, and analytics of Sauce Labs.`}</p>
    <p>{`Most importantly, by running these tests through Sauce Labs, you can:`}</p>
    <ul>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Run tests using popular JavaScript frameworks: `}<a parentName="li" {...{
          "href": "https://github.com/cypress-io/cypress"
        }}>{`Cypress`}</a>{`, `}<a parentName="li" {...{
          "href": "https://github.com/microsoft/playwright"
        }}>{`Playwright`}</a>{`, and `}<a parentName="li" {...{
          "href": "https://devexpress.github.io/testcafe"
        }}>{`TestCafe`}</a>{`.`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Take advantage of low latency provided by a containerized solution`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Review, share, and evaluate your test assets, such as logs, test results, and test videos `}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Use our Insights feature to perform deeper analysis of test outcomes`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Take advantage of other Sauce-specific options as development continues, including VMs, parallelization, and so on`}</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "how-to-get-started"
    }}>{`How to Get Started`}</h2>
    <p>{`To get started quickly, please see `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "/testrunner-toolkit/installation"
      }}>{`this page`}</a>{`.`}</p>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "how-it-works"
    }}>{`How it Works`}</h2>
    <p>{`Testrunner Toolkit achieves JavaScript framework testing through the combination of Sauce Labs, Jest, and the
JavaScript framework of your choice. `}</p>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "supported-frameworks-and-browsers"
    }}>{`Supported Frameworks and Browsers`}</h3>
    <p>{`In the current beta, the toolkit supports the following frameworks: `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "https://github.com/cypress-io/cypress"
      }}>{`Cypress`}</a>{`, `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "https://github.com/microsoft/playwright"
      }}>{`Playwright`}</a>{`, and `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "https://github.com/DevExpress/testcafe"
      }}>{`TestCafe`}</a>{`. The specific framework you use for testing depends on the types of tests you
need to run, and the environment where you run the tests.`}</p>
    <p>{`Furthermore, the framework and browser version support depends on the Sauce Labs docker images. The table below indicates framework and browser support based on the requisite docker image tag.`}</p>
    <div {...{
      "className": "admonition admonition-note alert alert--secondary"
    }}><div parentName="div" {...{
        "className": "admonition-heading"
      }}><h5 parentName="div"><span parentName="h5" {...{
            "className": "admonition-icon"
          }}><svg parentName="span" {...{
              "xmlns": "http://www.w3.org/2000/svg",
              "width": "14",
              "height": "16",
              "viewBox": "0 0 14 16"
            }}><path parentName="svg" {...{
                "fillRule": "evenodd",
                "d": "M6.3 5.69a.942.942 0 0 1-.28-.7c0-.28.09-.52.28-.7.19-.18.42-.28.7-.28.28 0 .52.09.7.28.18.19.28.42.28.7 0 .28-.09.52-.28.7a1 1 0 0 1-.7.3c-.28 0-.52-.11-.7-.3zM8 7.99c-.02-.25-.11-.48-.31-.69-.2-.19-.42-.3-.69-.31H6c-.27.02-.48.13-.69.31-.2.2-.3.44-.31.69h1v3c.02.27.11.5.31.69.2.2.42.31.69.31h1c.27 0 .48-.11.69-.31.2-.19.3-.42.31-.69H8V7.98v.01zM7 2.3c-3.14 0-5.7 2.54-5.7 5.68 0 3.14 2.56 5.7 5.7 5.7s5.7-2.55 5.7-5.7c0-3.15-2.56-5.69-5.7-5.69v.01zM7 .98c3.86 0 7 3.14 7 7s-3.14 7-7 7-7-3.12-7-7 3.14-7 7-7z"
              }}></path></svg></span>{`note`}</h5></div><div parentName="div" {...{
        "className": "admonition-content"
      }}><p parentName="div">{`Each docker image tag is the 'latest' image that supports the specific framework version`}</p></div></div>
    <Tabs defaultValue="cypress" values={[{
      label: 'Cypress',
      value: 'cypress'
    }, {
      label: 'Playwright',
      value: 'playwright'
    }, {
      label: 'TestCafe',
      value: 'testcafe'
    }]} mdxType="Tabs">

      <TabItem value="cypress" mdxType="TabItem">
        <table>
          <thead parentName="table">
            <tr parentName="thead">
              <th parentName="tr" {...{
                "align": null
              }}>{`Cypress Version`}</th>
              <th parentName="tr" {...{
                "align": null
              }}>{`Supported Browsers`}</th>
              <th parentName="tr" {...{
                "align": null
              }}>{`Release Notes`}</th>
              <th parentName="tr" {...{
                "align": null
              }}>{`Sauce Cloud Support [`}<a parentName="th" {...{
                  "href": "/testrunner-toolkit/running-tests#test-on-sauce-labs"
                }}>{`?`}</a>{`]`}</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody parentName="table">
            <tr parentName="tbody">
              <td parentName="tr" {...{
                "align": null
              }}>{`5.6.0`}</td>
              <td parentName="tr" {...{
                "align": null
              }}>{`Please see release notes.`}</td>
              <td parentName="tr" {...{
                "align": null
              }}><a parentName="td" {...{
                  "href": "https://github.com/saucelabs/sauce-cypress-runner/releases/tag/v5.7.3"
                }}>{`saucelabs/sauce-cypress-runner`}</a></td>
              <td parentName="tr" {...{
                "align": null
              }}>{`Windows 10`}</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </TabItem>
      <TabItem value="playwright" mdxType="TabItem">
        <table>
          <thead parentName="table">
            <tr parentName="thead">
              <th parentName="tr" {...{
                "align": null
              }}>{`Playwright Version`}</th>
              <th parentName="tr" {...{
                "align": null
