              <td parentName="tr" {...{
                "align": null
              }}><a parentName="td" {...{
                  "href": "https://github.com/saucelabs/sauce-testcafe-runner/releases/tag/v0.1.16"
                }}>{`saucelabs/sauce-testcafe-runner`}</a></td>
              <td parentName="tr" {...{
                "align": null
              }}></td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </TabItem>
    </Tabs> 
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "workflow-overview"
    }}>{`Workflow Overview`}</h3>
    <p>{`Below are the general steps for executing tests with Testrunner Toolkit. For further information, follow the links below:`}</p>
    <ul>
      <li parentName="ul"><a parentName="li" {...{
          "href": "/testrunner-toolkit/installation#installing-testrunner-toolkit"
        }}>{`Download and Install`}</a>{` `}<inlineCode parentName="li">{`saucectl`}</inlineCode></li>
      <li parentName="ul"><a parentName="li" {...{
          "href": "/testrunner-toolkit/configuration#authenticate"
        }}>{`Authenticate with your Sauce Labs Credentials`}</a></li>
      <li parentName="ul"><a parentName="li" {...{
          "href": "/testrunner-toolkit/configuration#generate-a-configuration-file-and-tests"
        }}>{`Generate a Configuration File and Tests Directory`}</a></li>
      <li parentName="ul"><a parentName="li" {...{
          "href": "/testrunner-toolkit/configuration#run-the-test"
        }}>{`Run the Tests`}</a></li>
      <li parentName="ul"><a parentName="li" {...{
          "href": "/testrunner-toolkit/configuration#analyze-test-results-in-sauce-labs"
        }}>{`Analyze Test Results on Sauce Labs`}</a></li>
    </ul>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "common-use-cases"
    }}>{`Common Use Cases`}</h2>
    <p>{`Below are some example user journeys and use cases that Testrunner Toolkit supports.`}</p>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "sample-tests"
    }}>{`Sample Tests`}</h3>
    <p>{`If you're starting from scratch and don't have any tests currently running as a part of your development workflow, `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`saucectl`}</inlineCode>{` will automatically `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "/testrunner-toolkit/configuration#choose-a-framework"
      }}>{`generate an example test when you choose an automation framework and run the initial command`}</a>{`. From there you can modify or expand upon the existing test.`}</p>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "existing-tests"
    }}>{`Existing Tests`}</h3>
    <p>{`If you already have existing tests in your project (like say in `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`cypress`}</inlineCode>{` for example), you can simply `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "testrunner-toolkit/installation#installing-testrunner-toolkit"
      }}>{`download and install `}<inlineCode parentName="a">{`saucectl`}</inlineCode></a>{`, `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "/testrunner-toolkit/configuration#modifying-the-configuration-file"
      }}>{`modify the existing configuration`}</a>{`, and `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "/testrunner-toolkit/running-tests#automation-framework-examples"
      }}>{`run your existing tests`}</a>{`.`}</p>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "pipeline-tests"
    }}>{`Pipeline Tests`}</h3>
    <p>{`If you wish to run `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`saucectl`}</inlineCode>{` as part of your DevOps CI toolchain, you can add it in your workflow by following one of our `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "/testrunner-toolkit/integrations"
      }}>{`CI integration guides`}</a>{`.`}</p>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "additional-resources"
    }}>{`Additional Resources`}</h2>
    <p>{`To learn more about the tools associated with this project please see the links below:`}</p>
    <ul>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Jest: `}<a parentName="li" {...{
          "href": "https://jestjs.io/"
        }}>{`https://jestjs.io/`}</a></li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Cypress: `}<a parentName="li" {...{
          "href": "https://github.com/cypress-io/cypress"
        }}>{`https://github.com/cypress-io/cypress`}</a></li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`The Microsoft Playwright project: `}<a parentName="li" {...{
          "href": "https://github.com/microsoft/playwright"
        }}>{`https://github.com/microsoft/playwright`}</a></li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`TestCafe: `}<a parentName="li" {...{
          "href": "https://devexpress.github.io/testcafe/"
        }}>{`https://devexpress.github.io/testcafe/`}</a></li>
    </ul>
    <p>{`Visit the links below to view information and release notes regarding the docker images' contents:`}</p>
    <ul>
      <li parentName="ul"><a parentName="li" {...{
          "href": "https://github.com/saucelabs/sauce-cypress-runner"
        }}>{`sauce-cypress-runner`}</a></li>
      <li parentName="ul"><a parentName="li" {...{
          "href": "https://github.com/saucelabs/sauce-playwright-runner"
        }}>{`sauce-playwright-runner`}</a></li>
      <li parentName="ul"><a parentName="li" {...{
          "href": "https://github.com/saucelabs/sauce-testcafe-runner"
        }}>{`sauce-testcafe-runner`}</a></li>
    </ul>
